Sentencas: The various composite cathode layers on the solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) with a dense electrolyte of yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) are investigated in this study.
Titulo: Fabrication and evaluation of electrochemical characteristics of the composite cathode layers for the anode-supported solid-oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The ceramic powders of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-delta (LSCF), Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.2Fe0.8O3-delta (BSCF), La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O3-delta (LSGM), and Gd0.2Ce0.8O3-delta (GDC) are prepared by the glycine-nitrate combustion process.
Titulo: Fabrication and evaluation of electrochemical characteristics of the composite cathode layers for the anode-supported solid-oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The different formations of composite cathode layers are coated onto the NiO-YSZ/YSZ half-cells via a screen printing method.
Titulo: Fabrication and evaluation of electrochemical characteristics of the composite cathode layers for the anode-supported solid-oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Scanning electron microscopy (SEM) micrographs show that all of the samples can be well adherent to the YSZ electrolyte.
Titulo: Fabrication and evaluation of electrochemical characteristics of the composite cathode layers for the anode-supported solid-oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: From the energy dispersive X-ray (EDX) result, the undesired compound of SrZrO3 is formed between the YSZ electrolyte and the composite cathode layers with LSCF and BSCF at the sintering temperature of 1000 degrees C.
Titulo: Fabrication and evaluation of electrochemical characteristics of the composite cathode layers for the anode-supported solid-oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: According to the results of the electrochemical test and electrochemical impedance spectroscopy (EIS), the composite cathode layer with YSZ-La0.8Sr0.2MnO3-delta (LSM) interlayer exhibits the best electrochemical performance.
Titulo: Fabrication and evaluation of electrochemical characteristics of the composite cathode layers for the anode-supported solid-oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The maximum power density can achieve the value above 400 mW/cm(2) for the samples with YSZ LSM interlayer.
Titulo: Fabrication and evaluation of electrochemical characteristics of the composite cathode layers for the anode-supported solid-oxide fuel cells
